========================================================================
                            I. Requirements
========================================================================
Web Server (Apache2)
PHP 5 >= 5.1.2, PECL hash >= 1.1
MySQL
   * MySQL user must have these privileges:
     CREATE, DROP, DELETE, INSERT, ALTER, UPDATE, SELECT
========================================================================


========================================================================
                        II. Installation
========================================================================
1. Decompress the files.
2. Use a text editor to edit the config.php file.
3. Use a web browser to navigate to the install.php page.
4. Click the Install button to begin the installation.
5. When the installation is done, login at the manage.php page using the
   default administrator and change your password.
